::Striker::

Striker's eyes widen as he hears Spears' words. The chip seemed to have had 
more of an effect that he had thought it would.

"Who's Preborn?"

His systems reported that his shoulder blasters were functionaly, his jetpack 
almost ready.

"Can you let me out?"
